{"tid":2102031,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"路透：拜登若當選將評估美國從德撤軍決定 並尋求應對中國威脅","createTime":"2020-07-10T07:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T01:25:32.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"2fb747400323e1792890d3b33a954586bc749d66","tid":2102031,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"路透7月9日 - 美國民主黨總統候選人拜登一位高級助手對路透表示，如果拜登當選，將評估總統特朗普從德國撤出數千名士兵的決定。<br />\n<br />\n「我們將評估特朗普做出的所有決定，包括這個，」拜登對外政策高級顧問Antony Blinken週三在接受專訪時表示。<br />\n<br />\n「當然是從其決定方式開始，」他補充稱，指的是特朗普在行動前沒有與德國溝通。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\nBlinken表示，拜登將試圖利用北大西洋公約組織(NATO)來處理中國對全球安全的威脅，其中可能包括處理中國華為在德國和英國等歐洲國家幫助建設5G通信網絡的作為。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n拜登嚴厲批評特朗普對待盟國的方式。他誓言強化NATO，並一再預言如果特朗普連任成功，包括美國與德國在內的西方安全聯盟可能走向終結。<br />\n<br />\n「總統對待NATO&mdash;世界歷史上最重要的軍事聯盟&mdash;像是對待一個勒索保護費組織，」拜登4月在一場籌資活動中表示，他在其他場合也提出類似表態。<br />\n<br />\n在週三路透專訪中，拜登的顧問認為，若重新強化歐美聯盟，有可能成為應對中國影響力的重要管道。<br />\n<br />\n「我們希望與歐洲盟友進行對話，討論中國給大西洋兩岸地區的安全帶來的一些挑戰，」奧巴馬政府前國家安全官員、拜登競選團隊顧問Julianne Smith稱。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-election-biden-germany-exclusive/exclusive-biden-to-review-trump-decision-to-cut-troops-in-germany-if-elected-idUSKBN24A293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-election-biden-germany-exclusive%2Fexclusive-biden-to-review-trump-decision-to-cut-troops-in-germany-if-elected-idUSKBN24A293&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwummlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=0aa31c0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-usa-election-biden-germany-exclusive%2Fexclusive-biden-to-review-trump-decision-to-cut-troops-in-germany-if-elected-idUSKBN24A293&h=5de1f81c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-usa-election-biden-germany-exclusive/exclusive-biden-to-review-trump-decision-to-cut-troops-in-germany-if-elected-idUSKBN24A293</a>"},{"pid":"c649d6063a171d5ca06efd44d5b98e61e31973d2","tid":2102031,"uid":57671,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:03:46.000Z","msg":"聽日後日記得投票<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYaAEA4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYaAEA4.jpg&h=f73580f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aFBTrf5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaFBTrf5.jpg&h=5dd3e3aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JApxGPq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJApxGPq.jpg&h=a84e2f7f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b5KUU9r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb5KUU9r.jpg&h=59996e90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tv5g8ur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftv5g8ur.jpg&h=666c3bcb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b0a4db2563430e4bd8c9a96d581fafec400daec","tid":2102031,"uid":158270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:44:28.000Z","msg":"向中國投誠"},{"pid":"e9d96f0d1f1941663d579eb83f16f8781df7c2f3","tid":2102031,"uid":51583,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:48:34.000Z","msg":"方法唔同<br />\n拜登會多d盟友<br />\n侵就成日得罪盟友咁<br />\n但侵又硬淨d"},{"pid":"d542a23bb2fe5ff9d177835fe8876941a58ae172","tid":2102031,"uid":92353,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:49:23.000Z","msg":"而家仲講開始尋求<br />\n侵侵直情做緊野 <br />\n唔係侵侵開左個頭 <br />\n拜登政綱邊有呢啲野"},{"pid":"317f30298b08f063460ca26c61810041c06ed59f","tid":2102031,"uid":121146,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d542a23bb2fe5ff9d177835fe8876941a58ae172","tid":2102031,"uid":92353,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:49:23.000Z","msg":"而家仲講開始尋求<br />\n侵侵直情做緊野 <br />\n唔